# Token pipeline ownership rules

## Files owned by Tokens Studio (never edit)
- tokens/**/*.json is written exclusively by the Tokens Studio Figma plugin.
- Never create, edit, rename, or delete files in tokens/.
- If a token value looks wrong (a weight, a color, a font name), do NOT fix it
  here. Flag it to me and I will change it in the Tokens Studio plugin, which
  is the source of truth. A hand edit here will be silently overwritten by the
  plugin's next push.

## Generated files (never edit, never commit)
- src/tokens/colors.ts and src/tokens/variables.css are generated by
  scripts/build-tokens.mjs. They are gitignored and rebuilt on every publish.
- Never edit them directly. To change their output, change the token JSON
  (via the plugin) or the build script.
- If they are missing or stale locally, run: npm run build:tokens

## Everything else
- Components, scripts, configs, and docs are owned by this editor. Edit freely.
- When adding a new component, reference tokens via the generated CSS variables
  (--ds-*) or the TypeScript exports. Never hardcode values that exist as tokens.